I've been having this problem a lot since F26 upgrade, too. I am now using FF53.0.3 binary from Mozilla I just downloaded. Seems better already, but can't be sure yet.
While using Firefox binary from mozilla.com, I haven't meet this bug again.
Let's switch to in-tree sqlite in next update - Firefox 54.

Okay, please reopen if you see such issue again.
